0in%20the%20Queens%20borough%20of%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bcdd107a3d27148877018d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20JetBlue%20Airbus%20A321neo.%3Cp%3EBruce%20Bennett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20California%20couple%20is%20suing%20JetBlue%20for%20%241%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20say%20a%20block%20of%20ice%20fell%20from%20a%20plane%20and%20crashed%20through%20their%20ceiling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20suit%20says%20they%20suffer%20from%20insomnia%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20planes%20flying%20overhead.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20is%20suing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjetblue-mint-first-class-suite-scared-of-flying-worth-it-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJetBlue%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%241%20million%2C%20saying%20that%20a%20block%20of%20ice%20fell%20from%20a%20plane%20and%20through%20their%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20complaint%20filed%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Michael%20Reese%20and%20Leah%20Ferrarini%20say%20they%20were%20in%20their%20Inglewood%2C%20California%20home%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjetblue-international-redeye-flight-what-its-like-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJetBlue%3C%2Fa%3E%20Airbus%20A321%20flying%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20New%20York%20passed%20overhead%20last%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20says%20that%20shortly%20after%208%20p.m.%2C%20a%20block%20of%20ice%20the%20size%20of%20a%20watermelon%20crashed%20through%20the%20roof%20and%20landed%20over%20their%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20police%20and%20the%20fire%20service%20were%20called%20to%20their%20home%2C%20and%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20launched%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20incident%2C%20Reese%20and%20Ferrarini%20would%20%26quot%3Bcringe%20in%20fear%20with%20each%20plane%20that%20passed%20over%20their%20home%20which%20is%20approximately%20one%20every%20five%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20sleep%20comfortably%20and%20suffer%20from%20insomnia.%20They%20are%20also%20looking%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20from%20their%20dream%20home%20because%20they%20no%20longer%20feel%20safe%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA's%20investigation%20found%20that%20the%20aircraft%20had%20a%20history%20of%20potable%20water%20issues%20dating%20back%20six%20months%2C%20the%20suit%20says.%20It%20adds%20that%20the%20same%20A321%20was%20suspected%20of%20dropping%20ice%20onto%20a%20home%20in%20Massachusetts%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETen%20days%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20inspections%20began%20on%20the%20plane's%20potable%20water%20system%2C%20where%20it%20was%20found%20that%20a%20valve%20flange%20was%20misaligned%2C%20causing%20a%20leak%2C%20per%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20accuse%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjetblue-mint-business-class-apartment-studio-jfk-edinburgh-scotland-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJetBlue%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20negligence%20and%20trespass%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20because%20they%20%26quot%3Bdid%20%3Cspan%3Enot%20grant%20JetBlue%20permission%20to%20allow%20the%20large%20chunk%20of%20ice%20to%20enter%20their%20home%20or%20cause%20damages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20asking%20for%20%24300%2C000%20for%20emotional%20distress%2C%20%24300%2C000%20for%20pain%2C%20suffering%2C%20and%20inconvenience%2C%20%2440%2C000%20in%20medical%20expenses%2C%20and%20%24360%2C000%20in%20property%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20filed%20in%20court%2C%20attorneys%20for%20JetBlue%20said%20the%20airline%20wasn't%20liable%20for%20the%20incident%20and%20its%20conduct%20was%20%26quot%3Bpursuant%20to%20statutes%2C%20governmental%20regulations%2C%20and%20industry%20standards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20asked%20that%20the%20airline%20be%20awarded%20the%20costs%20of%20the%20suit%20including%20attorneys'%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJetBlue%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20Business%20Insider%20outside%20US%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-sues-jetblue-1-million-says-ice-fell-through-ceiling-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459883000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678f7ba610c98eace9132347%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-sues-jetblue-1-million-says-ice-fell-through-ceiling-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michael%20Reese%20and%20Leah%20Ferrarini%20say%20they%20were%20at%20home%20when%20a%20block%20of%20ice%20fell%20from%20a%20JetBlue%20plane%20and%20crashed%20through%20their%20ceiling.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40businessinsider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-sues-jetblue-1-million-says-ice-fell-through-ceiling-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saif%20returns%20to%20residence%20after%20discharge%20from%20Lilavati%20hospital%20-%20See%20pics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117428334%2Cimgsize-87052.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsaif-ali-khan-returns-to-bandras-satguru-sharan-residence-after-discharge-from-lilavati-hospital-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F117428334.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20has%20returned%20home%20after%20a%20five-day%20hospitalization%20following%2