0425878916383%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20and%20drinking%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20going%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpcot%20hosts%20their%20culinary%20and%20wine%20festival%20every%20year.%20The%20festival%20ran%20from%20August%2029%20to%20November%2023%20in%202024.%20We%20already%20planned%20to%20visit%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20for%2010%20days%20last%20September%2C%20so%20it%20was%20perfect%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20my%20second%20Food%20and%20Wine%20Festival.%20The%20first%20was%20back%20in%202022%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Disney%20for%20a%20wedding%2C%20so%20didn't%20get%20the%20full%20experience.%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20take%20my%20time%20with%20entire%20days%20devoted%20to%20enjoying%20each%20country's%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8854ab3-ce18-4108-92cf-a18d69d1378c%5C%22%3EWe're%20a%20Disney%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20as%20part%20of%20a%20big%20group%20of%20family%20and%20friends%20(about%2014%20in%20total)%20and%20stayed%20in%20Disney's%20Yacht%20Club.%20The%20hotel%20was%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20Epcot%20%E2%80%94%20perfect%20for%20half-day%20trips%20and%20late-night%20visits.%20It%20meant%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20Ubers%20or%20driving%20home%20after%20a%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20recommend%20booking%20a%20hotel%20with%20easy%20transport%20to%20your%20favorite%20parks.%20Epcot%20is%20the%20most%20versatile%20for%20travel%2C%20with%20the%20Skyliner%2C%20Monorail%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20Friendship%20Boats%20all%20providing%20transport%20at%20this%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20pre-purchased%20our%20tickets%20with%20a%20deal%20of%2014%20days%20for%20the%20price%20of%20seven%2C%20which%20included%20the%20ability%20to%20park%20hop%20and%20a%20free%20Memory%20Maker%2C%20for%20%C2%A3549%20each%2C%20around%20%24669.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeptember%20tends%20to%20be%20quieter%20in%20the%20parks%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20very%20busy.%20The%20heat%20and%20humidity%20when%20we%20visited%20were%20tough.%20The%20festival%20was%20great%20because%20it%20gave%20us%20plenty%20of%20chances%20to%20stop%2C%20refuel%20and%20grab%20a%20cold%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee604a7d-1866-49ce-a313-0c5ad0102d5c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEpcot%20is%20an%20unmissable%20park%20for%20foodies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEpcot%20is%20the%20park%20best%20for%20foodies.%20During%20the%20festival%2C%20guests%20are%20encouraged%20to%20travel%20across%20the%20world%20by%20sampling%20food%20and%20drinks.%20These%20offerings%20are%20set%20up%20in%20little%20huts%20or%20stalls%2C%20mostly%20situated%20on%20the%20park's%20main%20pathways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20festival%20also%20puts%20on%20special%20events%20like%20live%20music%20and%20children's%20activities%20and%20sells%20unique%20merchandise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20first%20day%20in%20Epcot%2C%20we%20picked%20up%20a%20Festival%20Passport%20from%20the%20front%20of%20the%20park.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20details%20of%20each%20country's%20exclusive%20dishes%20and%20drinks%2C%20along%20with%20a%20stamp%20page%20for%20%26quot%3BEmile's%20Fromage%20Montage.%26quot%3B%20Guests%20who%20collected%20five%20stamps%20by%20purchasing%20featured%20dishes%20throughout%20the%20park%20won%20a%20prize.%20As%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20%26quot%3BRatatouille%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20was%20a%20must.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226cda13e-200e-4422-bd70-a91a44748da7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20researched%20the%20menus%20beforehand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20most%20dishes%20run%20from%20%244%20to%20%249%2C%20with%20the%20cost%20of%20beverages%20ranging%20a%20little%20wider%20due%20to%20a%20mix%20of%20non-alcoholic%20and%20alcoholic%20choices%2C%20smaller%20glasses%2C%20flights%2C%20and%20full-size%20cocktails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20our%20holiday%2C%20we%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20watching%20TikToks%20and%20deciding%20what%20dishes%20we'd%20try.%20Some%20dishes%20like%20the%20Fry