%20was%20welcomed%20by%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20%26quot%3Bit%20has%20been%20India's%20consistent%20and%20principled%20position%20that%20the%20Neutral%20Expert%20alone%20has%20the%20competence%20under%20the%20Treaty%20to%20decide%20these%20differences%26quot%3B%20pertaining%20to%20the%20Kishenganga%20and%20Ratle%20hydroelectric%20power%20plants%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20upholds%20and%20vindicates%20India's%20stand%20that%20all%20seven%20(07)%20questions%20that%20were%20referred%20to%20the%20Neutral%20Expert%2C%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20Kishenganga%20and%20Ratle%20hydroelectric%20projects%2C%20are%20differences%20falling%20within%20his%20competence%20under%20the%20Treaty%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20Pakistan%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20World%20Bank%20appointed%20a%20Neutral%20Expert%20and%20a%20chairman%20of%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20regarding%20the%20Kishenganga%20and%20Ratle%20hydroelectric%20power%20plants%2C%20in%20view%20of%20disagreements%20and%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20over%20the%201960%20Indus%20Water%20Treaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20treaty%2C%20signed%20after%20nine%20years%20of%20negotiations%2C%20with%20the%20Washington-based%20World%20Bank%20being%20a%20signatory%2C%20sets%20out%20a%20mechanism%20for%20cooperation%20and%20information%20exchange%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20regarding%20their%20use%20of%20the%20rivers.%20However%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20disagree%20over%20whether%20the%20technical%20design%20features%20of%20Kishenganga%20and%20Ratle%20hydroelectric%20power%20plants%20contravene%20the%20treaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20asked%20the%20World%20Bank%20to%20facilitate%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20to%20consider%20its%20concerns%20about%20the%20designs%20of%20the%20two%20hydroelectric%20power%20projects%2C%20while%20India%20asked%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20Neutral%20Expert%20to%20consider%20similar%20concerns%20over%20the%20two%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Neutral%20Expert%20said%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20carefully%20considered%20and%20analysed%20the%20Parties'%20submissions...%20The%20Neutral%20Expert%20accordingly%20finds%20that%20he%20should%20proceed%20to%20render%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20Points%20of%20Difference.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20light%20of%20the%20foregoing%2C%20the%20Neutral%20Expert%20also%20finds%20no%20need%20to%20address%20Pakistan's%20second%20alternative%20submission%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%2C%20the%20MEA%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20upheld%20his%20own%20competence%2C%20which%20comports%20with%20India's%20view%2C%20the%20Neutral%20Expert%20will%20now%20proceed%20to%20the%20next%20(merits)%20phase%20of%20his%20proceeding.%20This%20phase%20will%20culminate%20in%20a%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20each%20of%20the%20seven%20differences.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Neutral%20Expert%20process%20so%20that%20the%20differences%20are%20resolved%20in%20a%20manner%20consistent%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Treaty%2C%20which%20does%20not%20provide%20for%20parallel%20proceedings%20on%20the%20same%20set%20of%20issues.%20It%20added%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20recognise%20or%20participate%20in%20the%20illegally%20constituted%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20proceedings.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Governments%20of%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20also%20remain%20in%20touch%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20modification%20and%20review%20of%20the%20Indus%20Waters%20Treaty%2C%20under%20Article%20XII%20(3)%20of%20the%20Treaty%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-08%2Findus-water-treaty_650x400_61502353073.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneutral-expert-upholds-india-position-against-pakistan-over-hydro-projects-indus-water-treaty-7525222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20World%20Bank-appointed%20Neutral%20Expert%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20competent%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20differences%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20over%20two%20hydropower%20projects%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20under%20the%20Indus%20Water%20Treaty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UCO%20Bank's%20Q3FY25%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20rises%2027%25%20on%20better%20margins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Fuco-bank-s-q3fy25-results-net-profit-rises-27-on-better-margins-125012101003_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Plans%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20QIP%20in%20the%20current%20quarter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20to%20take%20back%2018k%20citizens%20residing%20illegally%20from%20US%20to%20placate%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459285000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Findia-to-take-back-18k-citizens-residing-illegally-from-us-to-placate-trump-125012100997_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20countries%20have%20together%20identified%20some%2018%2C000%20illegal%20Indian%20migrants%20in%20the%20US%20to%20be%20sent%20back%20home%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Can%20BCCI's%2010%20Diktats%20End%20Team%20India's%20Superstar%20Culture%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhichever%20way%20you%20might%20wish%20to%20want%20to%20see%20it%2C%20the%20BCCI's%20list%20of%2010%20commandments%2C%20the%20biggest%20talking%20point%20in%20cricketing%20circles%20currently%2C%20aimed%20at%20maintaining%20an%20egalitarian%20cricketing%20sub-society%2C%20ironically%20tells%20us%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98superstar%20culture'%20that%20has%20set%20in%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20clear%20right%20off%20the%20bat%20is%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20rules%20existed%20earlier%20too%2C%20under%20previous%20captains.%20There%20is%20no%20archive%20material%20available%20that%20suggests%20that%20the%20rules%20were%20officially%20changed.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20some%20players%20decided%20to%20do%20things%20their%20own%20way%20and%20were%20not%20stopped%20by%20anyone%20in%20charge.%20Clearly%2C%20these%20players%20thought%20that%20the%20rules%20didn't%20apply%20to%20them%2C%20or%2C%20worse%2C%20that%20they%20were%20powerful%20enough%20to%20go%20against%20the%20system.%20That%20is%20a%20definite%20problem%20area.%20Former%20India%20cricketers%20like%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20and%20Irfan%20Pathan%20have%20echoed%20similar%20sentiments.%20Harbhajan%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20went%20on%20record%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20least%20nine%20out%20of%2010%20points%E2%80%A6are%20the%20same%20%5Bfrom%20his%20time%20as%20an%20active%20cricketer%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%2010%20Diktats%20Are%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20now%2C%20everyone%20who%20tracks%20Indian%20cricket%20will%20be%20well%20aware%20of%20what%20the%2010%20commandments%20are.%20There%20are%20some%20that%20stand%20out%20because%20they%20are%20significant%2C%20like%20players%20making%20themselves%20available%20for%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20travelling%20with%20the%20team%20for%20matches%2C%20tours%20and%20practice%20sessions%2C%20complete%20availability%20for%20all%20scheduled%20practice%20sessions%2C%20and%20staying%20on%20with%20the%20team%20even%20if%20Test%20matches%20end%20before%20the%20scheduled%20end%20dates.%20These%20are%20rules%20that%20players%20should%20be%20following%20no%20matter%20what.%20Maintaining%20a%20certain%20team%20spirit%20is%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20clearly%2C%20not%20everyone%20sees%20it%20that%20way%20perhaps.%20With%20the%20Indian%20team%20having%20gone%20through%20a%20nightmare%20time%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20especially%20of%20late%2C%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20have%20decided%20that%20the%20players%20need%20to%20be%20reminded%20in%20an%20official%20manner%20about%20a%20few%20rules%20that%20haven't%20been%20followed%20down%20to%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20tightrope%20to%20walk%2C%20even%20for%20the%20Board.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20superstar%20culture%20exists%20because%20the%20players%20have%20been%20elevated%20to%20the%20level%20of%20superstars.%20No%20one%20said%20anything%20about%20following%20these%20rules%20when%20the%20team%20was%20consistently%20doing%20well%E2%80%94at%20home%20and%20abroad%20in%20a%20country%20like%20Australia%E2%80%94where%20they%20won%20two%20back-to-back%20Test%20series%20before%20the%20last%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBCCI%20Getting%20Tough%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar's%20comment%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20not%20a%20school%2C%20it's%20not%20punishment%E2%80%9D%2C%20referring%20to%20the%2010-point%20list%2C%20further%20highlights%20the%20conundrum%20the%20people%20in%20charge%20must%20be%20experiencing%20right%20now.%20Stressing%20on%20%E2%80%9Cdiscipline%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cteam%20unity%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccohesion%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20team%20is%20going%20through%20a%20rough%20patch%20under%20a%20new%20coach%20might%20sound%20like%20a%20good%20plan%20to%20show%20to%20the%20world%20that%20the%20Board%20is%20cracking%20the%20whip%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20everybody%20in%20line%20(without%20ruffling%20any%20feathers)%2C%20but%20there%20are%20two%20problems%20with%20that.%20One%2C%20does%20the%20Board%20really%20think%20that%20reiterating%20basic%20rules%20will%20lift%20performance%20on%20the%20field%3F%20And%20two%2C%20if%20they%20actually%20think%20that%2C%20then%20why%20was%20this%20strict%20reminder%20not%20sent%20out%20earlier%3F%20Were%20they%20waiting%20for%20a%20lean%20phase%20to%20set%20in%20before%20reminding%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20superstars%20of%20the%20sport%20that%20cricket%20is%20a%20team%20game%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20quite%20a%20common%20occurrence.%20A%20kind%20of%20inertia%20sets%20in%20when%20things%20are%20going%20smoothly.%20As%20long%20as%20there%20is%20no%20emergency%20and%20results%20are%20sustained%2C%20the%20tendency%20is%20to%20let%20things%20continue%20the%20way%20they%20are%2C%20allowing%20people%20to%20do%20what%20they%20individually%20want%20to%20do.%20However%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20a%20dire%20need%20to%20change%20arises%2C%20one%20rushes%20to%20make%20sure%20all%20the%20rules%20are%20followed%2C%20down%20to%20the%20last%20detail.%20The%20question%2C%20though%2C%20that%20we%20have%20to%20ask%20here%20is%2C%20why%20aren't%20rules%20followed%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20smoothly%20things%20are%20going%3F%20Why%20must%20a%20team%20be%20reminded%20of%20some%20of%20the%20most%20basic%20rules%20of%20a%20team%20sport%2C%20like%20staying%20together%20as%20a%20group%20in%20the%20same%20team%20hotel%2C%20travelling%20on%20the%20same%20team%20bus%2C%20or%20not%20leaving%20for%20their%20homes%20if%20a%20match%20finishes%20early%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EMore%20To%20Domestic%20Cricket%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20credit%20where%20credit%20is%20due.%20The%20Indian%20men's%20senior%20cricket%20team%20needed%20a%20reminder%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98superstar%20culture'%20had%20to%20be%20curbed.%20Kudos%20to%20the%20people%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20meeting%20where%20this%2010-point%20list%20was%20drawn%20up%20again.%20The%20suggestion%20that%20players%20should%20make%20themselves%20available%20for%20domestic%20cricket%20whenever%20possible%20so%20as%20to%20stay%20eligible%20for%20national%20selection%20is%20critical.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20help%20in%20ending%20the%20%E2%80%98superstar%20culture'%2C%20but%20it%20also%20gives%20a%20boost%20to%20domestic%20cricket's%20structure.%20Imagine%20a%20Delhi%20vs%20Mumbai%20match%20with%20Virat%20and%20Pant%20squaring%20off%20against%20Rohit%20and%20Surya.%20Then%2C%20there's%20the%20valuable%20game%20time%20that%20out-of-form%20cricketers%20can%20leverage%20out%20of%20this.%20Players%20who%20play%20all%20three%20formats%20not%20wanting%20to%20get%20into%20domestic%20cricket%20while%20on%20a%20break%20is%20still%20understandable%2C%20but%20why%20players%20who%20are%20struggling%20to%20find%20form%20would%20want%20to%20fight%20this%20is%20beyond%20this%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20good%20to%20see%20Virat%20Kohli%20making%20himself%20available%20for%20the%20Delhi%20team%20for%20the%20last%20round%20of%20Ranji%20Trophy%20group%20matches.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20since%202012%20that%20he%20will%20turn%20up%20for%20a%20domestic%20match.%20Other%20star%20players%20like%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20have%20also%20made%20themselves%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPain%20Points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20other%20rules%2C%20like%20participation%20in%20official%20BCCI%20engagements%2C%20players%20paying%20for%20any%20separate%20arrangement%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20for%20their%20bags%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20excellence%2C%20and%20new%20excess%20baggage%20limits%20will%20not%20make%20anyone%20lose%20any%20sleep.%20But%20some%20others%2C%20like%20restrictions%20on%20personal%20staff%2C%20will%20need%20the%20players%20to%20get%20used%20to%20major%20logistical%20changes.%20A%20few%20reports%20have%20claimed%20that%20a%20certain%20player%20in%20the%20team%20has%20been%20known%20to%20travel%20with%20his%20personal%20chef%2C%20while%20another%20with%20bodyguards%20and%20a%20nanny%20for%20his%20children.%20The%20Board%20wants%20to%20end%20this.%20Clearly%2C%20BCCI%20officials%20feel%20that%20a%20return%20to%20the%20original%20protocol%20will%20allow%20players%20to%20focus%20on%20only%20the%20job%20at%20hand%20and%20help%20them%20see%20each%20other%20as%20a%20team%20and%20not%20just%20as%20individuals%20who%20come%20together%20on%20the%20field%20to%20play%20a%20team%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20bone%20of%20contention%20though%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20diktat%20that%20on%20tours%20of%2045%20days%20or%20more%2C%20players'%20partners%20and%20families%20can't%20stay%20with%20them%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20and%20that%20they%20can't%20accompany%20players%20at%20all%20during%20the%20first%20two%20weeks%20of%20the%20tour.%20On%20shorter%20tours%2C%20families%20can%20stay%20with%20the%20players%20for%20up%20to%20a%20week.%20Not%20surprisingly%2C%20media%20reports%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20players%20are%20not%20very%20happy%20with%20this.%20In%20fact%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20heard%20talking%20to%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20about%20it%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20where%20the%20squads%20for%20the%20ODI%20leg%20of%20the%20England%20home%20series%20and%20the%20upcoming%20Champions%20Trophy%20were%20announced.%20The%20Indian%20captain%20thought%20that%20the%20microphone%20was%20switched%20off%20and%20was%20heard%20telling%20the%20chief%20selector%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20have%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20BCCI%20Secretary%2C%20Devajit%20Saikia%2C%20about%20the%20restrictions%20on%20families%20travelling%20with%20the%20team.%20He%20also%20mentioned%20how%20multiple%20players%20have%20talked%20to%20him%20about%20this%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20players%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Rules%20Are%20Rules'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20however%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20new%20rule%20and%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20part%20of%20players'%20contracts.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20in%202018%2C%20the%20then%20captain%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20had%20requested%20that%20this%20rule%20be%20relaxed.%20The%20rule%20was%20eased%20off%20quite%20a%20bit%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20players%20were%20given%20the%20choice%20to%20induct%20their%20families%20in%20the%20team%20bubble%20on%20mental%20health%20grounds.%20It%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20hear%20what%20Gautam%20Gambhir's%20views%20are%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20one%20is%20a%20tough%20rule%20to%20debate%2C%20after%20all.%20Different%20things%20work%20for%20different%20players.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20rule%20has%20to%20be%20the%20same%20for%20everyone.%20Let's%20just%20hope%20that%20the%20re-emphasis%20on%20and%20implementation%20of%20these%20diktats%20doesn't%20deepen%20any%20rifts%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%20at%20a%20time%20when%20consolidation%20is%20key.%20A%20lot%20is%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fq67mfngo_team-india-afp_625x300_14_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%2