%20these%20are%20not%20issues%20that%20should%20be%20discussed%20and%20debated.%20These%20are%20issues%20that%20one%20can%20introspect%20on%2C%20one%20can%20ingest%20and%20one%20can%20come%20to%20some%20conclusion%20and%20do%20whatever%20they%20want.%20That's%20all%20to%20it.%20There's%20nobody%20who%20can%20say%2C%20you%20should%20do%20it%2C%20you%20should%20not%20do%20it%2C%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Murthy%20said%20at%20the%20Kilachand%20Memorial%20Lecture%20in%20Mumbai%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20former%20tech%20boss%20had%20earlier%20said%20India's%20young%20workforce%20has%20to%20embrace%20hard%20work%20if%20they%20want%20the%20country%20to%20realise%20its%20full%20potential%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20podcast%20in%20October%202023%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20work%20productivity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20Unless%20we%20improve%20our%20work%20productivity%2C%20unless%20we%20reduce%20corruption%20in%20the%20government%20at%20some%20level%2C%20because%20we%20have%20been%20reading%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20the%20truth%20of%20it%2C%20unless%20we%20reduce%20the%20delays%20in%20our%20bureaucracy%20in%20taking%20this%20decision%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20those%20countries%20that%20have%20made%20tremendous%20progress.%20So%20therefore%2C%20my%20request%20is%20that%20our%20youngsters%20must%20say%20'this%20is%20my%20country.%20I'd%20like%20to%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week'.%26quot%3B%20He%20had%20cited%20examples%20of%20the%20Germans%20and%20Japanese%20during%20World%20War%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20had%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%20as%20a%20section%20of%20social%20media%20users%20said%20such%20a%20remark%20from%20an%20industry%20leader%20will%20lead%20to%20exploitation%20of%20employees%20and%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20work-life%20balance.%20Many%20pointed%20out%20that%20expecting%20such%20work%20output%20from%20entry%20level%20employees%20with%20low%20wages%20was%20unfair%2C%20while%20others%20said%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20quality%2C%20and%20not%20quantity%2C%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20over%20work-life%20balance%20was%20stoked%20earlier%20this%20month%20when%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%20chairman%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%20spoke%20about%20a%2090-hour%20workweek.%20During%20an%20internal%20interaction%2C%20Mr%20Subrahmanyan%20was%20asked%20why%20L%26amp%3BT%20required%20its%20employees%20to%20work%20on%20Saturdays.%20He%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20regret%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20make%20you%20work%20on%20Sundays%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%20If%20I%20can%20make%20you%20work%20on%20Sundays%2C%20I%20will%20be%20more%20happy%2C%20because%20I%20work%20on%20Sundays%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%20sitting%20at%20home%3F%20How%20long%20can%20you%20stare%20at%20your%20wife%3F%20How%20long%20can%20the%20wives%20stare%20at%20their%20husbands%3F%20Get%20to%20the%20office%20and%20start%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20L%26amp%3BT%20chairman%20shared%20an%20anecdote.%20He%20spoke%20of%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20Chinese%20person%20China%20could%20surpass%20the%20US%20because%20of%20the%20country's%20strong%20work%20ethics.%20Quoting%20the%20Chinese%20person%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BChinese%20people%20work%2090%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20while%20Americans%20work%20only%2050%20hours%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%20Drawing%20a%20parallel%2C%20he%20encouraged%20L%26amp%3BT%20employees%20to%20follow%20a%20similar%20work%20regimen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20drew%20a%20wave%20of%20criticism%2C%20prompting%20L%26amp%3BT's%20HR%20head%20Sonica%20Muraleedharan%20to%20issue%20a%20statement.%20She%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btruly%20disheartening%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20how%20the%20words%20Mr%20Subrahmanyan%20were%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20been%20present%20during%20the%20internal%20address%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20state%20that%20SNS%20never%20implied%20or%20mandated%2090-hour%20work%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20work-life%20balance%20debate%2C%20industrialist%20Gautam%20Adani%20shared%20his%20take%20on%20it.%20%26quot%3BYour%20work-life%20balance%20should%20not%20be%20imposed%20on%20me%2C%20and%20my%20work-life%20balance%20shouldn't%20be%20imposed%20on%20you.%20Say%2C%20someone%20spends%20four%20hours%20with%20family%20and%20finds%20joy%20in%20it%2C%20or%20if%20someone%20else%20spends%20eight%20hours%20and%20enjoys%20it%2C%20that's%20their%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajaj%20Auto%20Managing%20Director%20Rajiv%20Bajaj%20weighed%20in%20too.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20a%2090-hour%20week%2C%20start%20from%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20CNBC-TV18.%20%26quot%3BNumber%20of%20hours%20of%20work%20doesn't%20matter%2C%20quality%20of%20work%20does.%20We%20need%20a%20kinder%2C%20gentler%20world%20more%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fb9na25qo_narayana-murthy_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-work-life-balance-nobody-can-say-you-should-do-it-narayana-murthys-latest-on-work-hours-7525213%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20co-founder%20Narayana%20Murthy%2C%20whose%20call%20for%20a%2070-hour%20work%20week%20had%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%2C%20has%20now%20said%20no%20one%20should%20impose%20long%20work%20hours%20on%20another%20person%20and%20stressed%20that%20these%20are%20issues%20not%20for%20debate%2C%20but%20for%20introspection.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mouth%20freshener%20brand%20JoySpoon's%20funding%20round%20reaches%20Rs%201