of%20the%20injuries%20was%20on%20his%20spine%20and%20doctors%20said%20the%20knife%20missed%20his%20spinal%20cord%20by%20just%202%20mm.%20The%20spinal%20fluid%2C%20however%2C%20had%20leaked%20out%20and%20a%20surgery%20was%20conducted%20to%20fix%20this.%20The%20actor%20also%20underwent%20plastic%20surgery%20for%20injuries%20on%20his%20arm%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEliyama%20Philip%2C%20who%20looks%20for%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20sons%20Taimur%20and%20Jeh%2C%20has%20told%20police%20that%20she%20was%20the%20first%20to%20spot%20the%20intruder.%20She%20has%20said%20she%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20some%20noises%20around%202%20am.%20She%20saw%20the%20bathroom%20door%20ajar%20and%20the%20light%20on%20and%20assumed%20that%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20was%20checking%20on%20Jeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20then%20I%20went%20back%20to%20sleep%20but%2C%20again%2C%20I%20realised%20something%20was%20wrong.%20So%20I%20woke%20up%20again%20and%20saw%20a%20man%20come%20out%20of%20the%20bathroom%20and%20go%20into%20the%20boy's%20room.%20I%20quickly%20got%20up%20and%20went%20to%20Jeh's%20room.%20The%20attacker%20then%20put%20his%20finger%20near%20his%20mouth%20and%20said%20'Don't%20make%20any%20noise%2C%20nobody%20will%20go%20out'%20in%20Hindi%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Philip%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20rushed%20to%20pick%20up%20Jeh%2C%20the%20man%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20wooden%20stick%20and%20a%20long%20Hexa%20blade.%20ran%20towards%20me%20and%20tried%20attacking%20me.%20I%20tried%20to%20block%20the%20attack%20by%20putting%20my%20hand%20forward%2C%20but%20the%20blade%20hit%20me%20near%20the%20wrists%20of%20both%20my%20hands%20and%20on%20the%20middle%20finger%20of%20my%20left%20hand.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20'What%20do%20you%20want%3F'.%20He%20said%2C%20'I%20want%20money.'%20I%20asked%2C%20'How%20much%20do%20you%20want%3F'%20He%20said%20in%20English%2C%20'one%20crore'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Philip%20has%20said%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5