%20the%20kids%20are%20%26quot%3Bmore%20independent%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20can%20be%20a%20recipe%20for%20disaster.%20I%20feel%20stretched%20so%20thin%20right%20now%20trying%20to%20afford%20our%20lives%20when%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20my%20teens%20need%20me%20to%20be%20emotionally%20and%20physically%20present%20more%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-wasnt-prepared-for-how-expensive-teenage-years-can-be-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67882ae68951662c9f207271%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-wasnt-prepared-for-how-expensive-teenage-years-can-be-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20didn't%20plan%20for%20the%20exponential%20expense%20of%20parenting%20teenagers%20and%20part%20of%20me%20wonders%20if%20I%20did%20the%20right%20thing%20in%20my%20early%20days%20as%20a%20stay-at-home%20mom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chaunie%20Brusie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-wasnt-prepared-for-how-expensive-teenage-years-can-be-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aditya%20Birla%20Real%20Estate%20Q3%20results%3A%20Revenue%20falls%2016.7%25%20to%20Rs%20946.21%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737459044000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faditya-birla-real-estate-q3-results-revenue-falls-16-7-to-rs-946-21-cr-125012100996_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20incurred%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%2042.37%20crore%20in%20Q3%20FY25%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Masahiro%20Na