C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-inauguration-why-melania-trump-had-her-face-hidden-by-a-hat%2Farticleshow%2F117427701.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-inauguration-why-melania-trump-had-her-face-hidden-by-a-hat%2Famp_articleshow%2F117427701.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-inauguration-why-melania-trump-had-her-face-hidden-by-a-hat%2Famp_articleshow%2F117427701.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B26%25%20Of%20India's%20Workforce%20Exposed%20To%20AI%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gita%20Gopinath%20At%20Davos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%2026%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20workforce%2C%20across%20all%20industries%20and%20sectors%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bexposed%26quot%3B%20to%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20or%20AI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fgita-gopinath%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGita%20Gopinath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%2C%20told%20NDTV%20Tuesday%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fndtv-davos-33%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Switzerland's%20Davos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20all%20doom%20and%20gloom%2C%20since%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20those%20jobs%20will%20benefit%20from%20the%20introduction%20of%20AI%20and%20related%20technologies.%20The%2012%20per%20cent%20will%20battle%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisplacement%20effect%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20of%20course%2C%20there%20is%20the%20labour%20market%20impact.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20India%2C%20for%20example%2C%20our%20estimate%20is%20that%20about%2026%20per%20cent%20(of%20the%20workforce)%20is%20exposed%20to%20AI...%20but%2C%20of%20this%2C%20about%2014%20per%20cent%20will%20benefit%20and%20the%20remaining%2012%20per%20cent%20will%20have%20more%20of%20a%20'displacement%20effect'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20comments%20seem%20to%20agree%20with%20what%20Amitabh%20Kant%2C%20India's%20G20%20Sherpa%2C%20said%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20Mr%20Kant%20said%C2%A0that%20although%20the%20advance%20of%20is%20%26quot%3Binevitable%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20will%20bring%20in%20%26quot%3Bnew%20kinds%20of%20jobs...%20new%20scales%20of%20jobs%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20therefore%2C%20we%20need%20to%20create%20many%20more%20skilled%20people%20in%20these%20areas%20(referring%20to%20data%20sciences%2C%20machine%20learning%2C%20etc.)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fai-is-inevitable-will-bring-in-new-kinds-of-jobs-amitabh-kant-at-ndtv-world-summit-6848500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAI%20Inevitable%2C%20Will%20Bring%20New%20Kinds%20Of%20Jobs%26quot%3B%3A%20Amitabh%20Kant%20To%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20was%20a%20recurring%20topic%20at%20the%20NDTV%20Summit%2C%20right%20from%20the%20opening%20remarks%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20said%20his%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20increase%20AI%20use%20in%20each%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecond-ai-in-india-aspirational-india-pm-modi-at-ndtv-world-summit-6836601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20Has%20Double%20AI%20Power%26quot%3B%3A%20What%20PM%20Said%20At%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20Of%20AI%20On%20Global%20Economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gopinath%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20the%20overall%20impact%20(of%20AI)%20on%20global%20economies%2C%20to%20which%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty...%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20AI%20will%20do%20for%20economies.%20We%20have%20estimates%20for%20productivity%20being%20raised...%20which%20is%20between%200.1%20and%200.8%20per%20cent%20every%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20given%20world%20growth%20is%20three%20(per%20cent)%20on%20average%2C%20it%20is%20potentially%20a%20large%20impact.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20impact%20of%20AI%20on%20jobs%2C%20whether%20in%20India%20or%20other%20countries%2C%20Ms%20Gopinath%20indicated%2C%20will%20depend%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20rate%20of%20development%20and%20absorption%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20quickly%20governments%20facilitate%20its%20integration%20into%20jobs%20and%20the%20workspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20depends%20on%20what%20gets%20done...%20in%20terms%20of%20building%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20and%20skilling%20the%20workforce%20so%20they%20can%20use%20this%20new%20technology%2C%20as%20well%20as%20also%20having%20the%20right%20environment%20for%20innovation%20and%20starting%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20Growth%20Steady%20At%203.3%25%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20larger%20question%20of%20global%20growth%20-%20which%20the%20IMF%20has%20pegged%20at%20three%20to%203.5%20per%20cent%20for%202025%2F26%20-%20Ms%20Gopinath%20spoke%20of%20divergences%20and%20specific%20challenges%20faced%20by%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20more%20powerful%20economies%2C%20including%20India%2C%20China%2C%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20global%20growth%20holding%20steady%20at%20three%20to%203.5%20per%20cent...%20but%20this%20is%20quite%20divergent.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20we%20see%20the%20United%20States%20as%20quite%20strong%20and%20so%20we%20have%20upgraded%20its%20forecast%2C%20but%20we%20see%20Europe%20as%20somewhat%20weaker%20and%20China%20has%20its%20own%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20what%20countries%20need%20to%20do%20for%20balanced%20growth...%20this%20is%20pretty%20country-specific.%20For%20China%2C%20for%20example%2C%20lot%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20on%20the%20property%20sector%20and%20the%20need%20to%20bring%20up%20domestic%20demand.%20In%20Europe%20they%20have%20to%20take%20action%20to%20raise%20productivity%20to%20get%20growth%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fimf-chief-expects-global-uncertainty-in-2025-heres-what-she-said-on-india-7447970%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIMF%20Expects%20Global%20Uncertainty%20In%202025.%20On%20India%20It%20Said...%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20IMF%20leader%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20impact%20of%20global%20geopolitical%20tensions%20on%20the%20world's%20growth%20story%2C%20but%20adopted%20a%20realist%20position%20on%20that%20front%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20geopolitical%20tensions...%20that's%20something%20governments%20around%20the%20world%20have%20to%20deal%20with...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Slowdown%20Temporary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%2C%20however%2C%20much%20more%20optimistic%20about%20the%20India%20growth%20story%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20country%20remains%20the%20fastest%20growing%20major%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20even%20if%20the%20projected%20growth%20of%206.5%20per%20cent%20for%20this%20fiscal%20is%20lower%20than%20initially%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gopinath%20said%20this%20was%20due%20to%20a%20slow%20start%20to%20public%20investment%20after%20the%20federal%20election%20in%20April-June%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20India%20to%20bounce%20back...%20we're%20also%20seeing%20rural%20sector%20consumption%20strengthening%2C%20as