al%20today%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Priti%20Adani%2C%20and%20elder%20son%20Karan%20Adani%20in%20Prayagraj.%20At%20the%20event%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20said%20his%20youngest%20son%2C%20Jeet%20Adani%2C%20will%20get%20married%20on%20February%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJeet's%20marriage%20is%20on%207th%20February.%20Our%20activities%20are%20like%20common%20people.%20His%20marriage%20will%20be%20very%20simple%20and%20with%20fully%20traditional%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said%20to%20a%20question%20asked%20by%20the%20media%20about%20his%20son's%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Prayagraj%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%7C%20On%20his%20son%20Jeet%20Adani's%20marriage%2C%20Adani%20Group%20chairman%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BJeet's%20marriage%20is%20on%207th%20February.%20Our%20activities%20are%20like%20common%20people.%20His%20marriage%20will%20be%20very%20simple%20and%20with%20full%20traditional%20ways...%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCebEZ4q14i%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCebEZ4q14i%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1881635184443105556%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2021%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%20was%20asked%20whether%20Jeet%20Adani's%20wedding%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3BMaha%20Kumbh%20of%20celebrities%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20which%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBilkul%20nahi%20hoga%26quot%3B%20(No%2C%20it%20won't%20be).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeet%20Adani%20joined%20the%20Adani%20Group%20in%202019%2C%20after%20attending%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20-%20School%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Applied%20Sciences.%20He%20started%20his%20career%20in%20the