er%20or%20not%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20put%20up%20money%20for%20a%20vision%20of%20the%20future%20that%20is%20hardly%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ba155a4-95a8-4170-ab4a-306e38a2894d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%20for%20building%20AI%20infrastructure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20talking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677bfc6d6672fb592aeb2ea9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222481%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20is%20calling%20for%20more%20investment%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EEugene%20Gologursky%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20has%20offered%20no%20shortage%20of%20reasons%20for%20spending%20so%20much%20money%20on%20achieving%20superintelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20technological%20hegemony%20over%20China%20is%20one.%20As%20his%20company%20said%20last%20week%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20an%20estimated%20%24175%20billion%20sitting%20in%20global%20funds%20awaiting%20investment%20in%20AI%20projects%26quot%3B%20that%20%26quot%3Bwill%20flow%20to%20China-backed%20projects%26quot%3B%20and%20strengthen%20Beijing%20if%20not%20directed%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20is%20that%20superintelligence%20could%20unlock%20unimaginable%20prosperity%20for%20society.%20Altman%20recently%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20we%20could%20fast-forward%20a%20hundred%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prosperity%20from%20superintelligence%20would%20feel%20just%20as%20unimaginable%20as%20today's%20world%20would%20to%20a%20lamplighter%2C%20a%20person%20employed%20to%20light%20and%20maintain%20street%20lights%20until%20about%20the%201950s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20reason%20is%20perhaps%20more%20surprising.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.samaltman.com%2Freflections%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20blog%20published%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Altman%20said%20his%20company%20is%20now%20confident%20that%20it%20knows%20how%20to%20build%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20a%20term%20often%20interchanged%20with%20superintelligence%20despite%20their%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%20that%20will%2C%20in%20some%20way%2C%20have%20triggered%20the%20flood%20of%20comments%20from%20those%20who%20want%20to%20play%20their%20part%20in%20developing%20the%20infrastructure%20needed%20to%20deliver%20superintelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blog%20published%20this%20month%20titled%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.microsoft.com%2Fon-the-issues%2F2025%2F01%2F03%2Fthe-golden-opportunity-for-american-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Golden%20Opportunity%20for%20American%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Microsoft%20president%20Brad%20Smith%20said%20the%20company%20planned%20to%20spend%20%2480%20billion%20alone%20this%20year%20on%20data%20centers.%20%26quot%3BNot%20since%20the%20invention%20of%20electricity%20has%20the%20United%20States%20had%20the%20opportunity%20it%20has%20today%20to%20harness%20new%20technology%20to%20invigorate%20the%20nation's%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20in%20conjunction%20with%20BlackRock%20and%20others%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20unveiled%20a%20fund%20focused%20on%20AI%20infrastructure%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.microsoft.com%2F2024%2F09%2F17%2Fblackrock-global-infrastructure-partners-microsoft-and-mgx-launch-new-ai-partnership-to-invest-in-data-centers-and-supporting-power-infrastructure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20potential%20of%20up%20to%20%24100%20billion.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Farticle%2F12%2F12%2F2024%2Fwhy-alphabet-and-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-never-panicked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintervie