F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.txed.235070%2Fgov.uscourts.txed.235070.1.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esued%20the%20Nuclear%20Regulatory%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20claims%20that%20the%20government%20agency%20was%20applying%20the%20same%20risk%20analysis%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewcleo-coo-nuclear-startup-europe-small-modular-reactor-ipo-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%20modular%20reactors%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20it%20was%20to%20large-scale%20power%20plants.%20These%20SMRs%2C%20as%20they're%20known%2C%20are%20meant%20to%20make%20access%20to%20nuclear%20power%20cheaper%2C%20given%20their%20compactness%20and%20greater%20affordability%20versus%20traditional%20nuclear%20plants.%20But%20even%20these%20face%20roadblocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20big%20reason%20that%20investors%20may%20want%20to%20approach%20infrastructure%20investment%20with%20caution%20is%20that%20the%20emergence%20of%20superintelligence%20remains%20highly%20speculative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman's%20claim%20that%20there%20is%20now%20a%20clear%20path%20to%20AGI%20is%20worth%20taking%20seriously%2C%20as%20new%20models%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fdeliberative-alignment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20o3%20released%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E%20demonstrate%20increasingly%20sophisticated%20reasoning%20capabilities%20that%20do%20more%20than%20just%20parrot%20their%20training%20data.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20there%20have%20been%20rumblings%20across%20the%20industry%20recently%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-wall-scaling-laws-training-data-chatgpt-gemini-claude-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20models%20hitting%20a%20wall%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20terms%20of%20performance%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20really%20serious%20advances%20in%20capabilities%2C%20then%2C%20or%20a%20cl