s%2C%20of%20course%2C%20one%20of%20the%20known%20Davids.%20But%20if%20you%20really%20watch%20closely%2C%20then%20you%20have%20Anthropic%2C%20Mistral%2C%20etc.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShankar%20said%20that%20the%20coming%20years%20will%20reveal%20who%20the%20next%20%26quot%3BDavid%26quot%3B%20will%20be.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20the%20next%20few%20years%20are%20about%20watching%20some%20of%20these%20new-age%20players.%20They%20are%20going%20to%20scale%20up%2C%20and%20the%20velocity%20at%20which%20they%20do%20so%20will%20be%20different%20from%20the%20past.%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20a%20new%20David%20will%20emerge%20to%20take%20that%20space%20open.%26quot%3B%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Spriha%20Srivastava%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20people%20sit%20at%20a%20table%20with%20four%20white%20chairs%20beside%20a%20white%20wall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678f81b810c98eace91323cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAbhishek%20Shankar%2C%20president%20of%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20spoke%20to%20BI's%20Spriha%20Srivastava.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20a%20problem%20right%20now%3A%20it's%20forgetful.%20If%20you've%20ever%20had%20a%20long%20back-and-forth%20with%20a%20chatbot%20you%20may%20have%20noticed%20it%20sometimes%20can't%20recall%20information%20from%20earlier%20in%20your%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20booking%20firm%20Navan%20might%20not%20be%20the%20company%20you'd%20think%20would%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%20but%20its%20CTO%2C%20Ilan%20Twig%2C%20told%20BI%20he's%20created%20a%20new%20framework%20for%20AI%20that%20more%20closely%20mimics%20the%20human%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20it%20like%20different%20topic%20experts%20that%20are%20all%20talking%20to%20one%20another%20and%20passing%20information%20back%20and%20forth%20%E2%80%94%20one%20knows%20airline%20seating%2C%20another%20knows%20everything%20about%20your%20loyalty%20program%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20the%20user%2C%20it's%20as%20if%20they're%20just%20chatting%20to%20one%20person.%20If%20you've%20ever%20felt%20the%20frustration%20of%20dealing%20with%20a%20chatbot%20when%20your%20flight%20got%20delayed%2C%20or%20being%20passed%20through%20countless%20service%20agents%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwig%20said%20its%20travel%20agent%20is%20already%20dealing%20with%207%2C000%20chats%20a%20day%20and%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20inbound%20requests%20are%20solved%20without%20having%20to%20go%20through%20to%20a%20human.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Hugh%20Langley%20and%20Dan%20DeFrancesco%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ENacho%20De%20Marco%20had%20a%20funny%20remark%20when%20we%20asked%20him%20whether%20AI%20would%20hurt%20his%20business%2C%20BairesDev%2C%20which%20provides%20software%20engineering%20support%20to%20companies%20on%20an%20outsourcing%2Fstaff%20augmentation%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20some%20people%20say%20that%20about%20journalists%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Touche!%20This%20said%2C%20he%20predicted%20that%20in%20the%20next%20five%20to%20ten%20years%2C%20%26quot%3Bsoftware%20is%20going%20to%20become%20just%20a%20lot%20better%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20new%20technologies.%20%26quot%3BIn%2020%20years%2C%20I%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Jamie%20Heller%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20firm%20the%20size%20of%20KPMG%20looks%20to%20move%20into%20a%20new%20business%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20turn%20heads%2C%20but%20the%20Big%20Four%20professional-services%20firm's%20effort%20to%20set%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-law-us-arizona-application-big-four-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20US%20law%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20about%20upending%20the%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20its%20leaders.%20Paul%20Knopp%2C%20chair%20and%20CEO%20at%20KPMG%20US%2C%20told%20me%20the%20strategy%20is%20rounding%20out%20the%20type%20of%20services%20they're%20already%20doing.%20He%20mentioned%20things%20like%20addressing%20the%20legal%20issues%20that%20come%20with%20contract%20management%20or%20performing%20due%20diligence%20on%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20see%20it%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20traditional%20law%20firms%20that%20are%20out%20there%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Knopp%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20looking%20more%20for%20complimentary%20or%20adjacent%20services%20that%20fit%20well%20with%20what%20we're%20already%20doing%20that%20can%20add%20value%20to%20the%20particular%20service%20we're%20already%20providing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20how%20KPMG%20plans%20to%20staff%20the%20new%20group%2C%20Knopp%20said%20the%20firm%20will%20lean%20on%20the%20relationships%20it%20already%20has%20established%20recruiting%20directly%20out%20of%20universities.%20It'll%20also%20make%20what%20Knopp%20called%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20entry%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20the%20firm%20would%20hire%20people%20currently%20working%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20Knopp%20doesn't%20see%20that%20as%20a%20massive%20threat%20to%20mid-size%20and%20large%20law%20firms%20since%20the%20focus%20won't%20be%20on%20the%20type%20of%20litigation%20or%20regulatory%20work%20that%20those%20firms%20excel%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20very%20reason%20we're%20getting%20into%20that%20space.%20We%20think%20there's%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20unfilled%20need%20where%20we%20can%20serve%20in%20that%20capacity.%20Where%20there's%20some%20legal%20services%20that%20can%20be%20performed%20by%20us%20more%20efficiently%20because%20we%20know%20the%20other%20service%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20Knopp%20added.%20%E2%80%94%3Cem%3E%20Dan%20DeFrancesco%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20two%20blue%20bobblehats%20on%20a%20table%2C%20one%20slightly%20s