%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%20analysis%20found%20that%20social%20media%20management%2C%20e-commerce%20optimization%2C%20paid%20media%20advertising%2C%20performance%20marketing%2C%20and%20influencer%20marketing%20were%20among%20the%20fastest-growing%20skills%20people%20in%20the%20advertising%20and%20marketing%20industries%20have%20added%20to%20their%20profiles%20on%20the%20platform%20between%20January%202025%20and%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20marketers%20under%20pressure%20to%20measure%20ROI%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20it's%20no%20surprise%20that%20they%20are%20increasingly%20leaning%20into%20skills%20like%20influencer%20marketing%20to%20build%20trust%20with%20their%20audiences%20and%20drive%20continued%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tom%20Pepper%2C%20senior%20director%20at%20LinkedIn.%20(ROI%20refers%20to%20%26quot%3Breturn%20on%20investment%26quot%3B.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertising%20and%20marketing%20LinkedIn%20users%20were%20less%20likely%20to%20add%20established%20skills%20like%20%26quot%3Bmarketing%20communications%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20profiles%2C%20as%20well%20as%20skills%20like%20web%20design%20and%20email%20marketing%2C%20where%20AI%20is%20increasingly%20replacing%20human%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAutomation%20continues%20to%20squeeze%20PR%2C%20copywriting%2C%20media%20owner%20sales%2C%20and%20production%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Simon%20Francis%2C%20CEO%20of%20Flock%20Associates%2C%20a%20marketing%20consultancy%20and%20search%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertising%20recruiters%20said%20they%20are%20searching%20for%20candidates%20whose%20career%20paths%20have%20taken%20unusual%20or%20varied%20turns.%20This%20can%20sometimes%20indicate%20that%20they%20are%20adaptable%20to%20the%20industry's%20ever-changing%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20skillsets%2C%20