0proposition%20has%20been%20enticing%20to%20portfolio%20managers%20as%20well%20as%20prospective%20backers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20team%20is%20empowered%20and%20very%20independent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scolari%2C%20whose%20ties%20to%20the%20Agnelli%20family%20go%20back%20a%20generation%20to%20when%20his%20father%20worked%20as%20the%20head%20of%20research%20and%20development%20at%20Fiat%20decades%20ago.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20BI%2C%20he%20said%20the%20structure%20set%20the%20firm%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20really%20important%20%E2%80%94%20I%20really%20believe%20in%20this%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252816e39-b5cd-4b31-8ef6-abd1c2e7d92f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20different%20model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20doesn't%20like%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bplatform%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it's%20impossible%20to%20avoid%20comparisons%20between%20today's%20dominant%20multistrategy%20managers%20and%20Lingotto.%20These%20platforms%20have%20become%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20alternative%20investing%2C%20in%20part%20because%20they%20can%20absorb%20so%20much%20capital%20from%20sovereign%20wealth%20funds%20and%20pensions%20and%20diversify%20it%20across%20dozens%20of%20investing%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry's%20biggest%20investors%20prefer%20multistrategy%20funds%20because%20of%20their%20consistency%20and%20lack%20of%20volatility%2C%20which%20they%20achieve%20through%20tight%20risk%20limits%20and%20short-term%20investment%20horizons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELingotto%20employs%20multiple%20investors%20who%20operate%20quasi-independently%20of%20each%20other%2C%20like%20Citadel%20and%20Millennium.%20But%20the%20similarities%20between%20Lingotto%20and%20the%20biggest%20hedge%20funds%20end%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Lingotto%2C%20the%20ultimate%20authority%20over%20its%20four%20strategies%20lies%20with%20the%20heads%20of%20said%20strategies.%20There's%20no%20firmwide%20chief%20investment%20officer%20but%20four%20different%20CIOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223309%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22James%20Anderson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678ad49110c98eace912fe31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224961%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Baillie%20Gifford%20partner%20James%20Anderson%20joined%20Lingotto%20in%202023.%3Cp%3ETaurat%20Hossain%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20autonomy%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20BI.%20He%20runs%20the%20firm's%20%24700%20million%20innovation%20strategy%20alongside%20Morgan%20Samet%2C%20the%20strategy's%20cohead%20who%20used%20to%20work%20for%20the%20value-investment%20shop%20Pzena%20and%20the%20private-equity%20firm%20THL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20innovation%20team%20plans%20to%20invest%20in%20companies%20across%20their%20life%20cycle%2C%20including%20when%20they%20are%20private%2C%20and%20hold%20them%20through%20volatile%20patches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20suffer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anderson%2C%20who%20was%20an%20early%20investor%20in%20Tesla%20and%20Amazon%20and%20a%20big%20believer%20in%20Nvidia's%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20we%20earn%20our%20returns%20is%20by%20being%20supporters%20of%20these%20companies%20during%20their%20downturns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long-term%20nature%20of%20the%20firm's%20capital%2C%20thanks%20to%20Exor's%20role%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20company%2C%20allows%20Anderson%20and%20Samet%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20firm's%20three%20other%20strategy%20heads%20%E2%80%94%20to%20worry%20less%20about%20short-term%20gains%20and%20more%20about%20long-term%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Morgan%20Samet%20and%20James%20Anderson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678ad9fc10c98eace912ff64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224098%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorgan%20Samet%20runs%20the%20firm's%20%24700%20million%20innovation%20strategy%20with%20Anderson.%3Cp%3ETaurat%20Hossain%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20scared%20of%20volatility%2C%26quot%3B%20Samet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20that%20as%20more%20of%20an%20opportunity%2C%20%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207c7f048-5207-446e-95a2-e0ea74e545e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgnelli%2C%20through%20and%20through%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20firm%20wants%20to%20be%20viewed%20as%20more%20than%20just%20the%20investment%20arm%20of%20the%20Agnelli%20family%20%E2%80%94%20and%20already%20has%20outside%20capital%20from%20the%20French%20insurer%20Cov%C3%A9a%20%E2%80%94%20Lingotto%20is%20the%20brainchild%20of%20Elkann%2C%20the%20billionaire%20heir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20public%20letter%20after%20the%20firm%20launched%2C%20Elkann%20quoted%20the%2018th-century%20philosopher%20Adam%20Smith%20to%20stress%20how%20his%20family%20would%20be%20investing%20alongside%20any%20outside%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbove%20all%2C%20we%20think%20and%20act%20as%20principals%20rather%20than%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20Lingotto%2C%20named%20after%20an%20iconic%20Fiat%20factory%20in%20Turin%2C%20Italy%2C%20with%20a%20rooftop%20test%20track%20that%20began%20operations%20in%201923%2C%20plans%20to%20grow%20through%20%26quot%3Bperformance%20rather%20than%20capital%20inflows%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20to%20run%20strategies%20for%20the%20firm%20were%20a%20pair%20of%20longtime%20family%20connections%2C%20Scolari%20and%20Srinivasan%2C%20who%20now%20run%20the%20intersection%20and%20horizon%20strategies%2C%20respectively.%20Scolari%20previously%20worked%20for%20Eton%20Park%2C%20the%20now%20shuttered%20hedge%20fund%20founded%20by%20the%20former%20Gold