aa603%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEY's%20EMEIA%20managing%20partner%20believes%20there%20are%20five%20short-term%20solutions%20for%20Europe's%20competitiveness%20problem.%3Cp%3EJacek%20Kadaj%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEurope's%20economy%20has%20a%20competitiveness%20and%20innovation%20problem.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20Trump%20administration%20and%20Chinese%20pressure%20will%20only%20squeeze%20the%20economic%20bloc%20harder.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20five%20things%20could%20help%20Europe%20drive%20innovation%2C%20according%20to%20EY's%20Europe%20boss%2C%20Julie%20Teigland.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20EY%20employees%20spend%20their%20days%20analyzing%20individual%20businesses%20or%20conducting%20audits%20for%20clients.%20But%20at%20the%20upper%20ends%20of%20the%20EY%20machine%2C%20its%20leaders%20are%20part%20of%20the%20global%20conversation%20%E2%80%94%20consultants%20to%20governments%20and%20industry%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJulie%20Teigland%2C%20the%20firm's%20managing%20partner%20for%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Africa%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20big%20business%20challenge%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-innovation-mario-draghi-rival-us-china-tech-superpower-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elack%20of%20competitiveness%20and%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20picture%20only%20looks%20set%20to%20become%20more%20complex%20as%20Europe%20is%20squeezed%20between%20the%20new%20Trump%20administration's%20expected%20tariff%20policy%20and%20Chinese%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20US%20GDP%20growth%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20significantly%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20Europe.%20The%20IMF%20forecasts%201%25%20growth%20in%20the%20euro%20area%20in%202025%2C%20compared%20to%202.7%25%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20the%20US%20going%20twice%20as%20fast%20as%20Europe.%20That%20creates%20a%20downward%20spiral%2C%26quot%3B%20Teigland%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeigland%20said%20she%20is%20trying%20to%20drive%20conversation%20around%20what%20Europe%20can%20do%20to%20change%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20million%20examples%20of%20go-getters%2C%20but%20if%20we%20don't%20give%20them%20the%20ecosystem%20they%20need%2C%20they%20won't%20be%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Teigland%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20believes%20there%20are%20five%20things%20Europe%20can%20do%20in%20the%20short%20term%20to%20drive%20innovation%20and%20be%20more%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d567934d-f552-4f4c-a398-4dfbd51f30df%5C%22%3E1.%20Clearer%20implementation%20of%20regulation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20last%20years%20the%20number%20of%20regulations%20and%20the%20length%20of%20the%20regulations%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%2C%26quot%3B%20Teigland%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20member%20country's%20market%20is%20different%2C%20but%20any%20time%20new%20legislation%20comes%20in%2C%20it%20can%20be%20implemented%20in%2027%20different%20ways%2C%20she%20said.%20To%20stop%20duplication%20and%20inefficiencies%2C%20the%20EU%20needs%20to%20create%20more%20alignment%20on%20implementation%20before%20signing%20laws%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219a3aa76-5933-4778-99cb-4e425a8cac3d%5C%22%3E2.%20Create%20a%20capital%20markets%20union%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20capital%20markets%20union%20(CMU)%20would%20create%20a%20single%20market%20for%20capital%20in%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20breaking%20down%20barriers%20that%20block%20cross-border%20investments%20and%20allowing%20nations%20to%20share%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20Europeans%20to%20invest%20in%20European%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Teigland%20told%20BI.%20Creating%20a%20CMU%20would%20%26quot%3Bunlock%20billions%26quot%3B%20to%20create%20more%20of%20an%20innovation%20ecosystem.%20She%20wants%20to%20see%20the%20EU%20unbundle%20fees%20and%20allow%20pension%20funds%20to%20invest%20in%20equities%20with%20its%20biggest%20markets%2C%20like%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20you%20not%20make%20that%20transparent%20and%20lower%20the%20cost%3F%20Why%20do%20European%20mutual%20funds%20have%20to%20be%20significantly%20more%20expensive%20than%20American%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221219%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Profile%20of%20EY's%20managing%20partner%20EMEIA%20Julie%20Teigland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678e792fae09223df2baac4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulie%20Teigland%20is%20EY's%20managing%20partner%20for%20Europe%2C%20Middle%20East%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Africa%20(EMEIA)%3Cp%3EEY%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254a4e45b-6cfe-4bee-9067-69a8d58f7e42%5C%22%3E3.%20Support%20European%20champions%20by%20changing%20the%20laws%20on%20anti-competition%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20create%20any%20European%20champions%20in%20any%20industry%2C%20especially%20not%20in%20tech.%20Why%3F%20Because%20we%20don't%20allow%20them%20to%20combine%20across%20borders%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Teigland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeigland%20said%20the%20way%20to%20foster%20%26quot%3Bchampions%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20companies%20that%20help%20Europe%20compete%20with%20other%20economic%20powers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20to%20find%20more%20balance%20between%20regulation%20that%20drives%20protectionism%20and%20ones%20that%20drive%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20laws%20on%20anti-competition%20need%20to%20be%20changed%2C%20particularly%20for%20larger%20companies%20in%20late-stage%20financing%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20all%20the%20things%20that%20have%20been%20knocked%20out%2C%20all%20the%20deals%20that%20have%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20table%20t