Managed%20under%20the%20India%20Inflection%20Opportunity%20Trust%2C%20BVF%20Series%203%20targets%20a%20total%20corpus%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore%2C%20including%20a%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20green-shoe%20option%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbharat-value-fund-series-3-secures-rs-1-250-cr-eyes-rs-2-500-crore-target-125012100773_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gen%20Z%20is%20turning%20into%20big-time%20mallrats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teens%20in%20a%20mall%20shopping%20and%20having%20fun.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678abb7e10c98eace912f3f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Pedro%20Nekoi%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20David%20Martin%20was%20showing%20a%20prospective%20tenant%20around%20Brickell%20City%20Centre%2C%20an%20open-air%20mall%20he%20helps%20manage%20in%20downtown%20Miami.%20The%20man%20was%20an%20executive%20from%20FP%20Movement%2C%20part%20of%20the%20bohemian%20clothing%20brand%20Free%20People%2C%20and%20Martin%20was%20hoping%20he%20would%20decide%20to%20lease%20a%20shop%20in%20the%20mall.%20Teens%20and%20young%20professionals%20have%20been%20drawn%20to%20Brickell's%20palm-tree-lined%20backdrops%20and%20distinctive%20glass%20and%20steel%20trellis%2C%20which%20are%20featured%20regularly%20on%20TikTok%2C%20along%20with%20the%20elaborate%20CrazyShake%20milkshakes%20from%20Black%20Tap%20Craft%20Burgers%20%26amp%3B%20Beer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20as%20Martin%20was%20showing%20the%20FP%20guy%20around%2C%20a%20man%20in%20his%20early%2020s%20strolled%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20look%2C%20I%20know%20that%20guy!%26quot%3B%20the%20executive%20told%20Martin.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20one%20of%20our%20influencers!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20serendipitous%20encounter%20signaled%20the%20mall's%20popularity%20with%20Gen%20Z%2C%20which%20was%20exactly%20what%20Martin%20needed%20to%20seal%20the%20deal.%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%20my%20job%20is%20done%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20thought.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20just%20send%20you%20the%20lease!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFP%20Movement%20ended%20up%20opening%20a%20store%20in%20Brickell%20a%20few%20months%20later.%20But%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20moment%20was%20also%20evidence%20of%20something%20bigger%3A%20The%20American%20mall%2C%20against%20all%20odds%2C%20is%20cool%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20after%20they%20were%20written%20off%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopping-mall-rise-fall-timeline-1950s-to-today-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecasualty%20of%20the%20online%20shopping%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20malls%20from%20the%20resorts%20of%20Arizona%20to%20the%20suburbs%20of%20New%20Jersey%20are%20bustling%20and%20vibrant.%20Vacancy%20rates%20are%20the%20lowest%20in%20two%20decades%2C%20and%20both%20visits%20and%20sales%20have%20been%20climbing%20steadily%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years.%20And%20while%20older%20shoppers%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20written%20off%20the%20mall%2C%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20are%20embracing%20them%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-investment-opportunity-shopping-center-strip-mall-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehip%20new%20hangout%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%202023%20survey%20by%20the%20International%20Council%20of%20Shopping%20Centers%2C%2060%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20said%20they%20visited%20malls%20just%20to%20socialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-malls-in-us-mall-of-america-american-dream-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELuxury%20malls%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Brickell%20are%20doing%20especially%20well%20with%20Gen%20Z.%20With%20their%20modern%20aesthetic%2C%20over-the-top%20dining%20options%2C%20and%20limited-edition%20events%2C%20they've%20become%20more%20than%20a%20chic%20place%20to%20socialize%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20digital%20lives%20of%20young%20shoppers.%20%26quot%3BGoing%20to%20a%20mall%20used%20to%20be%20an%20errand%2C%20and%20now%20it's%20a%20content%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Casey%20Lewis%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BAfter%20School%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20newsletter%20on%20consumer%20trends.%20%26quot%3BThe%20constant%20need%20to%20document%20one's%20life%20on%20social%20media%20has%20put%20a%20larger%20importance%20on%20the%20aesthetic%20appeal%20of%20places%20like%20malls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20today's%20young%20shoppers%2C%20the%20mall%20offers%20more%20than%20an%20Instagram%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20place%20to%20practice%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20got%20lost%20during%20the%20social%20isolation%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BSocial%20media%20helps%20us%20refine%20our%20taste%2C%20but%20the%20mall%20lets%20us%20experiment%20with%20who%20we%20are%20IRL%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Claire%20Lee%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Selleb%2C%20an%20online%20platform%20that%20tracks%20Zoomer%20spending%20habits.%20%26quot%3BBeyond%20providing%20a%20backdrop%20for%20content%2C%20it's%20where%20we%20can%20almost%20test-drive%20the%20personas%20we%20post%20about%20online.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20malls%20of%20old%20embraced%20sameness%20%E2%80%94%20you%20could%20always%20count%20on%20a%20Victoria's%20Secret%20and%20a%20Cinnabon%20%E2%80%94%20today's%20retail%20meccas%20want%20to%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20crowd.%20To%20succeed%20today%2C%20the%20mall%20has%20to%20be%20a%20%3Cem%3Edestination%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20young%20shoppers%2C%20something%20they'll%20go%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20experience.%20That's%20especially%20true%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20dining.%20At%20a%20handful%20of%20malls%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%20the%20star%20tenant%20is%20Din%20Tai%20Fung%2C%20a%20Taiwanese%20chain%20that's%20garnered%20a%20cult%20following%20for%20its%20soup%20dumplings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBesides%20being%20delicious%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20fun%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Arden%20Yum%2C%20a%20college%20student%20who%20planned%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Orange%20County%20around%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20Din%20Tai%20Fung%20outpost%20at%20the%20South%20Coast%20Plaza%20mall.%20%26quot%3BYou%20write%20down%20your%20order%20on%20the%20paper%20menu%2C%20mix%20your%20own%20sauce%2C%20and%20ask%20for%20secret%20menu%20items%2C%20like%20the%20sea%20salt%20foam%20with%20the%20chocolate%20xiao%20long%20bao%20that%20are%20filled%20with%20molten%20chocolate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20meal%20for%20the%20content%20gold%20it%20was%2C%20Yum%20and%20her%20friends%20snapped%20pictures%20of%20each%20dish%20before%20digging%20in.%20And%20since%20they%20were%20already%20at%20the%20mall%2C%20they%20did%20some%20shopping%2C%20too.%20While%20waiting%20for%20their%20table%2C%20Yum%20picked%20up%20a%20pair%20of%20sunglasses%20at%20Gentle%20Monster%2C%20a%20Korean%20optical%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelebrity%20partnerships%20have%20also%20helped%20position%20malls%20as%20destinations.%20In%202022%2C%20when%20the%20YouTube%20star%20MrBeast%20announced%20he%20would%20be%20opening%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-eating-at-mrbeast-burgers-first-physical-location-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20MrBeast%20Burger%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20American%20Dream%20megamall%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20fans%20lined%20up%20to%20try%20his%20smashburgers%20and%20meet%20their%20idol.%20Some%20had%20slept%20in%20the%20mall%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20two%20years%20later%2C%20the%20burger%20joint%20is%20still%20going%20strong.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20day%20at%2010%20a.m.%20there's%20a%20line%20to%20start%20eating%20burgers%20at%20this%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Paul%20Ghermezian%2C%20American%20Dream's%20chief%20operating%20officer.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20place%20people%20come%20into%20the%20building%20and%20ask%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20attention%20was%20something%20of%20a%20lifeline%20for%20American%20Dream%2C%20which%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-american-dream-new-jersey-mall-theme-parks-ski-slope-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ederailed%20by%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20a%20year%20after%20opening.%20Located%207%20miles%20from%20Midtown%20Manhattan%2C%20the%20shopping%20and%20entertainment%20complex%20includes%20North%20America's%20only%20indoor%20ski%20slope%2C%20a%20skating%20rink%2C%20a%20water%20park%2C%20and%20amusement%20park%20rides%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20some%20450%20retail%20stores.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20aggressive%20targeting%20of%20young%20shoppers%20has%20helped%20it%20find%20its%20footing%20financially.%20American%20Dream%20says%20that%202024%20was%20its%20busiest%20year%20yet%2C%20with%20an%2011%25%20increase%20in%20foot%20traffic.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOnce%20the%20epitome%20of%20artificiality%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sanitized%20simulacrum%20of%20the%20town%20square%20%E2%80%94%20America's%20malls%20now%20serve%20as%20one%20of%20the%20last%20vestiges%20of%20real-world%20authenticity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20of%20physical%20and%20digital%20are%20intertwined%2C%20and%20allowing%20the%20two%20to%20live%20together%20is%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghermezian%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20feel%20the%20wind%20on%20your%20face%20as%20you%20get%20splashed%20on%20the%20wave%20pool%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20be%20there%20in%20person.%20And%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20make%20some%20damn%20good%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20marketing%20perspective%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20malls%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-men-women-leisure-spending-habits-differ-report-shows-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etargeting%20young%20shoppers%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20high-end%20offerings.%20Studies%20show%20that%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-loves-expensive-groceries-snacks-erewhon-whole-foods-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esplurging%20more%20at%20their%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20previous%20generations%20did.%20The%20global%20consulting%20firm%20Bain%20predicts%20that%20Zoomers%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20nearly%20a%20third%20of%20all%20luxury%20sales%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScottsdale%20Fashion%20Square%2C%20a%20mall%20in%20suburban%20Arizona%2C%20saw%20foot%20traffic%20jump%20144%25%20after%20it%20opened%20five%20high-end%20restaurants%2C%20including%20a%20Nobu%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fashionsquare.com%2FPress%2FDetails%2F856051%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20luxury%20brands%20for%20men.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20deliver%20something%20youthful%20and%20exciting%20to%20the%20marketplace%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Kim%20Choukalas%2C%20who%20manages%20the%20mall's%20leasing.%20%26quot%3BThe%20instant%20gratification%20of%20buying%20at%20a%20brick-and-mortar%20location%20will%20never%20go%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Miami%2C%20the%20Brickell%20mall%20specializes%20in%20high-end%20retailers%2C%20like%20Marc%20Jacobs%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-polo-shirts-men%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELuca%20Faloni%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20it's%20also%20made%20a%20point%20of%20adding%20more%20accessible%20brands%2C%20like%20FP%20Movement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20high-low%20mix%20is%20the%20key%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Martin%2C%20the%20leasing%20manager.%20%26quot%3BYou%20might%20be%20drawn%20to%20something%20at%20Saks.%20But%20you%20can%20always%20afford%20something%20at%20Sephora%20or%20H%26amp%3BM.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosmetics%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-luxury-perfume-obsession-tiktok-fragrance-teen-boys-branding-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efragrance%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20another%20Zoomer%20favorite%20%E2%80%94%20are%20also%20a%20reliable%20draw.%20And%20while%20the%20entry-level%20cosmetics%20floor%20has%20long%20been%20a%20staple%20of%20department%20stores%2C%20today's%20shopping%20meccas%20are%20taking%20it%20up%20a%20notch.%20In%20the%20fall%2C%20Nordstrom%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20an%20anchor%20store%20for%20many%20malls%2C%20launched%20a%20young-adult%20beauty%20section%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20six%20locations.%20Kohl's%2C%20the%20top-ranked%20department%20store%20among%20Zoomers%20in%20a%20recent%20survey%2C%20has%20a%20partnership%20with%20Sephora%20that%20racked%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jsonline.com%2Fstory%2Fmoney%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2F09%2F09%2Ffive-changes-that-kohls-is-making-to-store-layouts-to-boost-sale%2F75071862007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.4%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20sales%20in%202023%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20play%20to%20young%20shoppers%2C%20malls%20have%20also%20amped%20up%20their%20schedule%20of%20in-person%20events.%20Brickell%20hosts%20pop-ups%20with%20local%20chefs.%20Scottsdale%20Fashion%20Square%20hosts%20a%20Monday%20Mixer%20series%20that%20includes%20sunset%20yoga%20on%20a%20rooftop.%20And%20the%20Mall%20of%20America%20%E2%80%94%20the%20nation's%20largest%20mall%20%E2%80%94%20has%20added%20a%20live-action%20game%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20days%2C%20none%20of%20the%20marketing%20ploys%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-in-person-events-build