ral%20Committee%20Member%20(CCM)%2C%20a%20top%20decision-making%20body%20within%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20key%20position%2C%20which%20made%20him%20privy%20to%20sensitive%20operations%20of%20the%20banned%20outfit%2C%20drew%20a%20bounty%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%20The%20value%20of%20the%20bounty%20also%20suggests%20how%20important%20a%20target%20he%20was%20for%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaoist-carrying-rs-1-crore-bounty-among-14-killed-in-chhattisgarh-gariaband-encounter-7522656%5C%22%3EMaoist%20With%201%20Crore%20Bounty%20Among%2020%20Killed%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Says%20%26quot%3BMajor%20Success%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChalapati%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20dense%20and%20impenetrable%20forests%20of%20Bastar.%20His%20security%20detail%20comprising%208-10%20personal%20guards%20bears%20a%20testament%20to%20his%20importance%20within%20the%20Maoist%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20advanced%20weaponry%20like%20AK-47s%20and%20SLR%20rifles%2C%20Chalapati%20was%20a%20frontline%20leader%20who%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20making%20strategies%20and%20leading%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fid%3D891375%26category%3Dembed%26autostart%3D1%26pWidth%3D650%26pHeight%3D403%26embed_type%3Dstory%26mute%3D1%26autostart%3D1%26mutestart%3Dtrue%26ctitle%3D1%26miniplayer%3D1%26cache%3D2022%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20tactical%20expertise%2C%20leadership%20skills%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20mobilise%20resources%20in%20challenging%20terrains%20earned%20him%20notoriety%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wanted%20Maoist%20leaders%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChalapati%20relocated%20his%20base%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20in%20view%20of%20increasing%20encounters%20in%20Abujhmad%2C%20to%20the%20Gariaband-Odisha%20