%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218636d1c-d58d-4262-861d-322370af4c82%5C%22%3ESelf-driving%20stops%20and%20starts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20recent%20preponderance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-self-driving-robotaxi-cars-without-drivers-amazing-tech-review-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriverless%20Waymo%20rides%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20self-driving%20technology%20has%20been%20in%20limbo%20across%20the%20auto%20industry%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20carmakers%20cut%20costs%20and%20focus%20investments%20on%20more%20near-term%20technology%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautomakers-back-to-the-drawing-board-ev-plans-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20traditional%20carmakers%20are%20rethinking%20expensive%20autonomous%20technology%20development%20after%20decades%20of%20piecemeal%20progress%20and%20no%20clear%20path%20to%20profitability%20%E2%80%94%20ceding%20ground%20to%20tech-first%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20will%20win%20the%20chip%20war%20that%20lives%20inside%20the%20dashboards%20of%20most%20cars%20remains%20an%20open%20question.%20But%20after%20CES%2C%20analysts%20are%20much%20closer%20to%20calling%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday's%20cars%20are%20chock-full%20of%20chips.%20Most%20are%20far%20less%20complicated%20than%20the%20kind%20needed%20to%20offload%20driving%20tasks%20to%20the%20computer.%20Nvidia's%20competition%20includes%20other%20automotive%20chip%20giants%20like%20Qualcomm%20and%20Israel's%20Mobileye%2C%20which%20develops%20microchips%20and%20other%20technologies%20for%20the%20automotive%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20converges%20with%20increased%20adoption%20of%20self-driving%20technology%2C%20Nvidia%20now%20appears%20to%20be%20taking%20the%20lead%2C%20according%20to%20Martin%20French%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20automotive%20consultancy%20Berylls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToyota%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20automaker%2C%20will%20use%20Nvidia's%20Orin%20chips%20and%20automotive%20operating%20system%20to%20power%20its%20next%20generation%20of%20driver-assist%20features%2C%20Huang%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrin%20is%20Nvidia's%20solution%20for%20putting%20the%20computing%20power%20and%20intelligence%20of%20AI%20inside%20a%20car.%20The%20system%20debuted%20in%202019%20and%20has%20developed%20into%20a%20more%20all-encompassing%20solution%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMercedez%20Benz%2C%20China's%20BYD%2C%20and%20many%20luxury%20EV%20makers%20have%20also%20adopted%20Orin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20are%20not%20fully%20self-driving%2C%20but%20the%20long%20road%20between%20cruise%20control%20and%20realizing%20the%20dream%20of%20sleeping%20in%20the%20back%20seat%20while%20a%20car%20drives%20itself%20will%20have%20many%20stops%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinning%20Toyota's%20business%20is%20a%20big%20deal.%20McKinsey%20estimates%20that%20the%20assisted%20and%20autonomous%20driving%20market%20could%20be%20worth%20%24400%20billion%20by%202035.%20Nvidia%20forecasts%20a%20%245%20billion%20run%20rate%20for%20its%20automotive%20business%20in%20fiscal%20year%202025%2C%20a%20five-fold%20increase%20in%20the%20company's%20automotive%20business%20from%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20also%20joining%20forces%20with%20trucking%20startup%20Aurora%20Innovation%20and%20automotive%20supplier%20Continental%20to%20deploy%20self-driving%20trucks%20%E2%80%94%20an%20announcement%20that%20sent%20Aurora's%20stock%20soaring%2035%25%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22464edf3b-f384-4a0c-b5d0-83bb708bb78e%5C%22%3EBeyond%20the%20data%20center%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20self-driving%20technology%2C%20which%20Huang%20frequently%20lauds%2C%20is%20trained%20on%20Nvidia%20GPUs.%20However%2C%20the%20chips%20that%20make%20Tesla's%20full-self-driving%20run%20are%20designed%20in-house%20and%20manufactured%20by%20Samsung.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20back%20as%202019%2C%20Tesla%20and%20Nvidia%20shared%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.nvidia.com%2Fblog%2Ftesla-self-driving%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccelerated%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20they've%20been%20on-and-off%20partners.%20Today%20the%20partnership%20is%20very%20much%20on%2C%20with%20Huang%20and%20Musk%20regularly%20trading%20praise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECementing%20relationships%20with%20Toyota%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20Aurora%20puts%20Nvidia%20in%20a%20good%20position%20to%20be%20the%20primary%20supplier%20of%20self-driving%20technology%20to%20the%20automotive%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20companies%20can%20provide%20chips%20for%20cars%20and%20also%20the%20chips%20to%20train%20the%20AI%20needed%20for%20self-driving%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20two-hour%20CES%20keynote%20presentation%20spanning%20humanoid%20robots%20to%20AI%20laptops%2C%20Philips%20Capital%20analysts%20called%20Nvidia's%20automotive%20offering%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20significant%26quot%3B%20revelation%20at%20the%20tentpole%20event.%20Averaging%20less%20than%202%25%20of%20total%20revenue%20in%20the%20first%20three%20quarters%20of%202024%2C%20Nvidia's%20automotive%20business%20still%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20its%20data%20center%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20company's%20February%202024%20earnings%20call%2C%20CFO%20Colette%20Kress%20said%20%241%20billion%20of%20the%20firm's%20data%20center%20revenue%2C%20which%20is%20reported%20separately%20from%20the%20automotive%20chip%20business%2C%20was%20attributable%20to%20automotive%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20absolutely%20positioning%20themselves%20as%20the%20leader%20for%20autonomous%20technologies%2C%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20French%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225125f3bc-b5fa-4fdc-9ace-1e6d8ba5ecb0%5C%22%3E'A%20shot%20in%20the%20arm'%20for%20self-driving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20major%20car%20companies%20have%20abandoned%20their%20expensive%20self-driving%20car%20projects%20to%20focus%20on%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-fully-autonomous-self-driving-cars-ceo-development-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFord%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Volkswagen%20pulled%20funding%20from%20now-defunct%20self-driving%20startup%20ArgoAI%20in%202022%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxis-general-motors-cruise-problems-tesla-elon-musk-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGM%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20at%20the%20end%20of%202024%20it%20would%20end%20its%20Cruise%20division's%20robotaxi%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20bad%20news%20around%20self-driving%20tech%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20been%20quite%20downbeat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20French.%20%26quot%3BNvidia%20has%20reversed%20that%20and%20just%20gave%20autonomous%20driving%20an%20absolute%20shot%20in%20the%20arm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20were%20growing%20impatient%20with%20the%20drag%20on%20car%20companies'%20profits%20and%20lacked%20faith%20in%20legacy%20automakers'%20ability%20to%20develop%20software%2C%20French%20said.%20What%20it%20took%20to%20get%20investors%20back%20on%20board%20with%20self-driving%20tech%20was%20to%20hear%20it%20from%20a%20tech%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Jensen%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20people%20in%20tech%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20up%20onstage%20and%20tell%20everyone%20autonomous%20driving%20is%20here%20and%20robotics%20are%20just%20around%20the%20corner%20holds%20a%20lot%20of%20weight%20with%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20French%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20is%20well-known%20for%20having%20an%20appetite%20for%20market-making%20%E2%80%94%20frequently%20saying%20he%20looks%20for%20%26quot%3Bzero-billion-dollar%20markets%26quot%3B%20to%20simultaneously%20create%20and%20conquer.%20The%20AV%20market%20could%20still%20yet%20be%20won%20by%20one%20company%2C%20according%20to%20French.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complex%20regulatory%20environment%2C%20the%20automotive%20industry%20often%20strives%20to%20find%20a%20single%20standard%20to%20follow%20on%20new%20tech.%20That%20usually%20creates%20a%20period%20of%20stiff%20competition%20as%20companies%20vie%20to%20develop%20the%20winning%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20electric%20vehicle%20charging%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20industry%20couldn't%20agree%20on%20a%20single%20charger%20type%2C%20leading%20to%20mismatched%20plugs%20and%20ports%20for%20EV%20drivers%20searching%20for%20juice.%20But%20in%202023%2C%20the%20industry%20finally%20coalesced%20around%20the%20North%20American%20Charging%20Standard%20chargers%20used%20by%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20AI%20has%20closed%20the%20technological%20space%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-robots-huamanoid-self-driving-cars-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-driving%20cars%20and%20robotics%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20entire%20auto%20industry%20is%20about%20to%20find%20out%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20part%20of%20Nvidia's%20next%20zero-billion%20dollar%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gains-self-driving-cars-automotive-ai-technology-toyota-aurora-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737450002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6781596b8951662c9f1fa056%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gains-self-driving-cars-automotive-ai-technology-toyota-aurora-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20look%20at%20Nvidia's%20role%20in%20enabling%20autonomous%20vehicles%20and%20giving%20the%20industry%20a%20%26quot%3Bshot%20in%20the%20arm%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20analyst%20said.%22%2C%22a