evenue-to-triple-to-rs-2-400-cr-cmd-125012100553_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parents%20Were%20Immigrants%2C%205%20Children%3A%20A%20Look%20At%20Donald%20Trump's%20Family%20Tree%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20Donald%20Trump%20returning%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20Trump%20family%20is%20back%20in%20the%20spotlight.%20A%20mix%20of%20public%20figures%2C%20private%20individuals%2C%20and%20scandal-makers%2C%20the%20Trumps%20have%20all%20the%20characteristics%20of%20a%20modern%20political%20dynasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20Donald%20Trump's%20family%20tree%2C%20from%20his%20immigrant%20roots%20to%20the%20next%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump's%20Parents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFred%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFred%20Trump%20(1905-1999)%20was%20the%20son%20of%20German%20immigrants.%20Born%20in%20the%20Bronx%2C%20he%20rose%20from%20construction%20to%20amass%20a%20real%20estate%20fortune%2C%20founding%20the%20Fred%20Trump%20Organisation%20in%20Queens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFred%20was%20accused%20of%20profiteering%2C%20tax%20fraud%2C%20and%20racial%20discrimination%20in%20housing%20policies%20-%20violations%20of%20the%20Fair%20Housing%20Act.%20In%201927%2C%20Fred%20was%20arrested%20for%20participating%20in%20a%20Ku%20Klux%20Klan%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMary%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%20MacLeod%20Trump%20(1912-2000)%20was%20a%20Scottish%20immigrant%20born%20on%20the%20Isle%20of%20Lewis.%20She%20came%20to%20the%20US%20in%201930%20with%20just%20%2450%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20house%20help%20before%20meeting%20Fred.%20The%20couple%20married%20in%201936%20and%20had%20five%20children%3A%20Maryanne%2C%20Fred%20Jr.%2C%20Elizabeth%2C%20Donald%2C%20and%20Robert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump's%20Siblings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaryanne%20Trump%20Barry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eldest%20sibling%2C%20Maryanne%20Trump%20Barry%20(1937-2023)%2C%20was%20a%20US%20federal%20judge%20who%20served%20for%20decades%2C%20including%20appointments%20under%20Presidents%20Reagan%20and%20Clinton.%20She%20was%20a%20critic%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20private%20conversations%20revealed%20by%20her%20niece%2C%20Mary%20Trump.%20She%20had%20one%20son%2C%20David%20William%20Desmond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFred%20Trump%20Jr%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFred%20Jr.%20(1938-1981)%20was%20the%20eldest%20son%20and%20Fred%20Sr.'s%20initial%20choice%20to%20lead%20the%20family%20business.%20However%2C%20his%20struggles%20with%20alcoholism%20derailed%20his%20career.%20He%20worked%20as%20a%20pilot%20before%20dying%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20at%2042.%20Fred%20Jr.%20had%20two%20children%2C%20Mary%20Trump%20and%20Fred%20Trump%20III.%20Mary%20later%20became%20a%20prominent%20critic%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EElizabeth%20Trump%20Grau%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201942%2C%20Elizabeth%20worked%20at%20J.P.%20Morgan%20and%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20private%20Trump%20siblings.%20Married%20to%20documentary%20producer%20James%20Grau%2C%20she%20lives%20in%20Palm%20Beach.%20They%20have%20no%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERobert%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20sibling%2C%20Robert%20Trump%20(1948-2020)%2C%20was%20a%20trusted%20ally%20of%20Donald%20and%20a%20senior%20executive%20at%20the%20Trump%20Organisation.%20He%20died%20in%202020.%20He%20was%20married%20twice%20and%20adopted%20one%20stepson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump's%20Wives%20and%20Children%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIvana%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20first%20wife%2C%20Ivana%20Trump%20(1949-2022)%2C%20was%20a%20Czech-American%20businesswoman%20and%20mother%20to%20three%20of%20his%20children.%20She%20died%20in%202022%20after%20a%20fatal%20fall%20in%20her%20home.%20Their%20children%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump%20Jr%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E(1977)%3A%20Executive%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20Trump%20Organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIvanka%20Trump%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(1981)%3A%20Former%20Senior%20Adviser%20to%20the%20President%2C%20married%20to%20Jared%20Kushner.%20They%20have%20three%20children%3A%20Arabella%2C%20Joseph%2C%20and%20Theodore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEric%20Trump%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(1984)%3A%20Executive%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20married%20to%20Lara%20Trump%2C%20with%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarla%20Maples%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald's%20second%20wife%2C%20Marla%20Maples%20(1963)%2C%20is%20an%20actress%20and%20television%20personality.%20They%20have%20one%20daughter%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETiffany%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(1993)%3A%20A%20Georgetown%20Law%20graduate%20who%20keeps%20a%20relatively%20low%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMelania%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20current%20wife%20and%20First%20Lady%20Melania%20Trump%20(1970)%2C%20is%20a%20Slovenian-American%20former%20model.%20Together%2C%20they%20have%20one%20son%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarron%20Trump%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(2006)%3A%20The%20youngest%20Trump%20child%2C%20Barron%2C%20lives%20with%20his%20parents%20and%20attends%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Extended%20Trump%20Family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%20Trump%20(1965)%3A%20Fred%20Jr.'s%20daughter%2C%20a%20psychologist%20and%20author%2C%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20family%20dysfunction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFred%20Trump%20III%20(1962)%3A%20Fred%20Jr.'s%20son%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20professional%2C%20leads%20a%20quiet%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJared%20Kushner%20(1981