Fmangrove-conservationists-ayush-sarda-murukesan-prasenjit-mandal-coasts-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esociety%20through%20environmental%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20into%20environmental%20activism%20began%20not%20in%20a%20classroom%2C%20or%20a%20conference%20hall%2C%20but%20on%20the%20fields%20where%20he%20grew%20up.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20he%20spent%20long%20summer%20afternoons%20in%20his%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20mango%20orchards%2C%20where%20over%2027%20species%20of%20mangoes%20grew.%20The%20trees%20provided%20shade%2C%20and%20the%20air%20was%20cool.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20as%20I%20grew%20older%2C%20I%20saw%20those%20fields%20vanish.%20All%20the%20species%20of%20mangoes%2C%20too%2C%20became%20just%20memories.%20I%20realised%20that%20if%20this%20is%20the%20condition%20in%20our%20village%2C%20it%20must%20be%20worse%20in%20cities.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20B%20Pharmacy%20days%2C%20he%20supported%20underprivileged%20children%20by%20raising%20money%20for%20their%20school%20fees.%20However%2C%20as%20he%20witnessed%20the%20increasing%20destruction%20of%20nature%2C%20he%20was%20deeply%20affected%2C%20feeling%20an%20undeniable%20urge%20to%20shift%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355522%2Fwater-hero-rambabu-tiwari-mann-ki-baat-bundelkhand-drought-pond-revival-jal-mitra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocus%20towards%20environmental%20causes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20bicycle%20diaries%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3