erns%E2%80%99%20pickles%20and%20curry%20pastes%20are%20exported%20to%20Canada%2C%20USA%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20time%20the%20brand%20is%20getting%20global%20love.%20Again%2C%20Nataline%20was%20way%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20when%20it%20came%20to%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201947%2C%20when%20the%20last%20of%20the%20British%20were%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%20disappointed%20that%20they%20would%20have%20to%20forego%20their%20delicious%20pickles%20and%20jams%2C%20Nataline%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20Mumbai-based%20merchant%20exporter%20who%20agreed%20to%20carry%20her%20pickles%20to%20the%20UK%20in%201949%20%E2%80%94%20thus%20laying%20the%20carpet%20for%20export%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20business%20as%20a%20woman%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%201920s%2C%20required%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20intrepidity.%20And%20Nataline%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned.%20Brian%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandmother%20used%20to%20work%20really%20hard.%20In%20those%20days%2C%20Pune%20was%20mostly%20jungle%20land.%20So%2C%20she%20would%20cycle%20to%20the%20market%20at%204.30%20am%20to%20buy%20the%20ingredients%20she%20needed%20and%20put%20it%20on%20a%20bullock%20cart%2C%20which%20would%20then%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20the%20factory%20to%20be%20cooked%20and%20processed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20would%20meticulously%20record%20her%20recipes%20in%20a%20book%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20archive%20of%20food%20memories%2C%20which%20the%20family%20still%20holds%20on%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECarrying%20on%20an%20alimentary%20legacy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFerns%E2%80%99%20Pickles%20has%20seen%20three%20generations%20of%20expertise.%20And%20Brian%